properties.name: Louth Canal and Waithe Beck
properties.river_sea: River Lud, Louth Canal, Waithe Beck
properties.description: Louth Canal from Louth to Tetney Lock, the Waithe Beck from Binbrook to Tetney Lock and their tributaries, including the River Lud in Louth. Tributaries may also affect Utterby and Covenham St Mary
